---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import AdContainer from '../components/layout/AdContainer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="History of Lorem Ipsum - Origin and Meaning"
  description="Discover the fascinating 2000-year history of Lorem Ipsum. Learn about its origins from Cicero's classical Latin text and how it became the industry standard for placeholder text."
  keywords={['lorem ipsum history', 'lorem ipsum origin', 'cicero lorem ipsum', 'lorem ipsum meaning', 'de finibus bonorum et malorum']}
>
  <div class="container">
    <article class="content-article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 class="article-title">The History of <span class="text-gradient">Lorem Ipsum</span></h1>
        <p class="article-subtitle">A 2000-year journey from classical Latin literature to modern design</p>
      </header>

      <div class="article-content">
        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>Origins: Cicero and Classical Latin</h2>
          <p>
            Contrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text. It has roots in a piece of classical
            Latin literature from <strong>45 BC</strong>, making it over 2000 years old.
          </p>
          <p>
            Lorem Ipsum comes from sections 1.10.32 and 1.10.33 of <em>"de Finibus Bonorum et Malorum"</em> (The
            Extremes of Good and Evil) by <strong>Marcus Tullius Cicero</strong>, written in 45 BC. This book is a
            treatise on the theory of ethics, very popular during the Renaissance.
          </p>
          <div class="info-box">
            <h3>About Cicero</h3>
            <p>
              Marcus Tullius Cicero (106 BC – 43 BC) was a Roman statesman, orator, lawyer, and philosopher. He is
              considered one of Rome's greatest orators and prose stylists. His influence on the Latin language was
              immense, and his works remain widely read today.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>The Discovery</h2>
          <p>
            The discovery of Lorem Ipsum's true origin is credited to <strong>Richard McClintock</strong>, a Latin
            scholar from Hampden-Sydney College in Virginia.
          </p>
          <p>
            In the 1980s, McClintock was intrigued by a passage of Lorem Ipsum and decided to investigate. He looked up
            one of the more obscure Latin words, <em>consectetur</em>, from a Lorem Ipsum passage. Going through cites
            of the word in classical literature, he discovered the undoubtable source.
          </p>
          <blockquote class="quote-box">
            "The passage experienced a surge in popularity during the 1960s when Letraset used it on their dry-transfer
            sheets, and again during the 90s as desktop publishers bundled the text with their software."
          </blockquote>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>The Standard Lorem Ipsum Passage</h2>
          <p>The first line of Lorem Ipsum, <em>"Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet..."</em>, comes from a line in section 1.10.32:</p>
          <div class="classic-text">
            <h3>Original Latin (Cicero, 45 BC)</h3>
            <p class="latin-text">
              "Sed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus error sit voluptatem accusantium doloremque laudantium, totam
              rem aperiam, eaque ipsa quae ab illo inventore veritatis et quasi architecto beatae vitae dicta sunt
              explicabo. Nemo enim ipsam voluptatem quia voluptas sit aspernatur aut odit aut fugit, sed quia
              consequuntur magni dolores eos qui ratione voluptatem sequi nesciunt."
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="classic-text">
            <h3>English Translation (H. Rackham, 1914)</h3>
            <p>
              "But I must explain to you how all this mistaken idea of denouncing pleasure and praising pain was born
              and I will give you a complete account of the system, and expound the actual teachings of the great
              explorer of the truth, the master-builder of human happiness. No one rejects, dislikes, or avoids pleasure
              itself, because it is pleasure, but because those who do not know how to pursue pleasure rationally
              encounter consequences that are extremely painful."
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>The Standard Lorem Ipsum (Since 1500s)</h2>
          <p>
            An unknown printer in the 15th century took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book.
            The resulting text has been used ever since:
          </p>
          <div class="classic-text highlight">
            <p class="standard-lorem">
              "Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et
              dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip
              ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu
              fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt
              mollit anim id est laborum."
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <AdContainer
          adSlot="3344556677"
          adFormat="rectangle"
          className="ad-content"
        />

        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>Modern Adoption</h2>
          <p>
            Lorem Ipsum gained widespread popularity in the 1960s with the release of <strong>Letraset sheets</strong>
            containing Lorem Ipsum passages. These dry-transfer sheets were used by designers and typesetters worldwide.
          </p>
          <p>
            The digital revolution further cemented Lorem Ipsum's place in design. Desktop publishing software like
            <strong>Aldus PageMaker</strong> (later Adobe PageMaker) included versions of Lorem Ipsum as default
            placeholder text.
          </p>
          <div class="timeline">
            <div class="timeline-item">
              <div class="timeline-year">45 BC</div>
              <div class="timeline-content">
                <h4>Original Text</h4>
                <p>Cicero writes "de Finibus Bonorum et Malorum"</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
              <div class="timeline-year">1500s</div>
              <div class="timeline-content">
                <h4>First Use</h4>
                <p>Unknown printer scrambles text for type specimen book</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
              <div class="timeline-year">1960s</div>
              <div class="timeline-content">
                <h4>Letraset Era</h4>
                <p>Lorem Ipsum popularized with dry-transfer sheets</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
              <div class="timeline-year">1980s</div>
              <div class="timeline-content">
                <h4>Discovery</h4>
                <p>Richard McClintock traces origin to Cicero</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
              <div class="timeline-year">1990s-Present</div>
              <div class="timeline-content">
                <h4>Digital Age</h4>
                <p>Bundled with desktop publishing and design software</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>Why It Endures</h2>
          <p>
            Lorem Ipsum has remained the industry standard for over 500 years for several reasons:
          </p>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>
              <strong>Natural Distribution</strong> - The text has a more-or-less normal distribution of letters,
              making it look like readable English
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Neutrality</strong> - Being in Latin, it doesn't distract viewers with readable content during
              design reviews
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Standardization</strong> - Everyone recognizes it as placeholder text, avoiding confusion
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Versatility</strong> - Works well for any type of content, from body text to headlines
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section cta-section">
          <h2>Try Our Lorem Ipsum Generator</h2>
          <p>
            Generate your own Lorem Ipsum text with our modern, fast generator. Multiple formats, keyboard shortcuts,
            and 100% free.
          </p>
          <a href="/" class="button button-primary">Generate Lorem Ipsum →</a>
          <p class="built-by">
            Built by <a href="https://bobadilla.tech/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Bobadilla Tech</a>
            — engineers who build fast, reliable developer tools.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .content-article {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 0 4rem;
  }

  .article-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
  }

  .article-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .article-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .article-content {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .content-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .content-section h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .content-section p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .ad-content {
    margin: 3rem auto;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .info-box {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .info-box h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .info-box p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .quote-box {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  .classic-text {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .classic-text.highlight {
    border: 2px solid var(--accent);
  }

  .classic-text h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .latin-text {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .standard-lorem {
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .timeline {
    margin: 2rem 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 100px;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  .timeline-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline-year {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 80px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-align: right;
  }

  .timeline-content {
    flex: 1;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline-content::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -21px;
    top: 8px;
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    border: 3px solid var(--bg-primary);
  }

  .timeline-content h4 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-content p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .feature-list li {
    padding: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-glass);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .built-by {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .built-by a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .built-by a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .article-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .article-subtitle {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .article-content {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .content-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .timeline::before {
      left: 70px;
    }

    .timeline-year {
      width: 60px;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
    }

    .timeline-content {
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    .classic-text {
      padding: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
